highlights.text: “Rasiya” by Pritam, Shreya Ghoshal, and TUSHAR JOSHI is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Guwahati, up 37 spots at #13.
Pritam has the most spots on Top Songs Guwahati. “Kesariya” is the highest at #1.
“Dandelions” by Ruth B. has been on Top Songs Guwahati the longest, at 51 weeks straight.
